{"snp4.4:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 4.4 ","snp4.4:0.2":"Suddhatthakasutta ","snp4.4:1.1":"Passami suddham paramam arogam, ","snp4.4:1.2":"Ditthena samsuddhi narassa hoti; ","snp4.4:1.3":"Evabhijanam paramanti natva, ","snp4.4:1.4":"Suddhanupassiti pacceti nanam. ","snp4.4:2.1":"Ditthena ce suddhi narassa hoti, ","snp4.4:2.2":"Nanena va so pajahati dukkham; ","snp4.4:2.3":"Annena so sujjhati sopadhiko, ","snp4.4:2.4":"Ditthi hi nam pava tatha vadanam. ","snp4.4:3.1":"Na brahmano annato suddhimaha, ","snp4.4:3.2":"Ditthe sute silavate mute va; ","snp4.4:3.3":"Punne ca pape ca anupalitto, ","snp4.4:3.4":"Attanjaho nayidha pakubbamano. ","snp4.4:4.1":"Purimam pahaya aparam sitase, ","snp4.4:4.2":"Ejanuga te na taranti sangam; ","snp4.4:4.3":"Te uggahayanti nirassajanti, ","snp4.4:4.4":"Kapiva sakham pamuncam gahayam. ","snp4.4:5.1":"Sayam samadaya vatani jantu, ","snp4.4:5.2":"Uccavacam gacchati sannasatto; ","snp4.4:5.3":"Vidva ca vedehi samecca dhammam, ","snp4.4:5.4":"Na uccavacam gacchati bhuripanno. ","snp4.4:6.1":"Sa sabbadhammesu visenibhuto, ","snp4.4:6.2":"Yam kinci dittham va sutam mutam va; ","snp4.4:6.3":"Tameva dassim vivatam carantam, ","snp4.4:6.4":"Kenidha lokasmi vikappayeyya. ","snp4.4:7.1":"Na kappayanti na purekkharonti, ","snp4.4:7.2":"Accantasuddhiti na te vadanti; ","snp4.4:7.3":"Adanagantham gathitam visajja, ","snp4.4:7.4":"Asam na kubbanti kuhinci loke. ","snp4.4:8.1":"Simatigo brahmano tassa natthi, ","snp4.4:8.2":"Natva va disva va samuggahitam; ","snp4.4:8.3":"Na ragaragi na viragaratto, ","snp4.4:8.4":"Tassidha natthi paramuggahitanti. ","snp4.4:8.5":"Suddhatthakasuttam catuttham. "}